  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.3 送入神經網路的輸入處理\n",
    "\n",
    "雖然 RNN 是可以處理不同長度的輸入, 在寫程式時我們還是要\n",
    "\n",
    "* 設輸入文字長度的上限\n",
    "* 把每段文字都弄成一樣長, 太短的後面補上 0"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from keras.preprocessing import sequence"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x_train = sequence.pad_sequences(x_train, maxlen=100)\n",
